senses.sense_definition: A unitary authority and borough of Essex, England.

examples.text: The local council in <w>Thurrock</w> has approved the new development plan.
She decided to move to <w>Thurrock</w> to be closer to her relatives in Essex.

senses.sense_definition: The hold of a ship; also, the bilge.

examples.text: The sailors hurried to pump the rising water out of the <w>thurrock</w>.
Supplies were stored deep in the <w>thurrock</w> to keep the vessel stable.
